---
title: Super Green Salmon Couscous Bowl with Creamy Pesto
description: Bright, fresh and packed with goodness - this couscous bowl is a flavour powerhouse! Flaky, perfectly cooked salmon
sits atop a bed of fluffy couscous packed full of all your favourite veg, tied together with a dreamy drizzle of creamy
pesto dressing. It’s wholesome, satisfying and just the right amount of fancy!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
